1
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:38,720
♪The waves of sword dance send out ripples♪

2
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:41,560
♪I weather the raging storm to chase after the victorious banner♪

3
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:44,920
♪The snow is not concerned with joy or sadness♪

4
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:47,920
♪The horse rein I have been holding falls apart in the desert♪

5
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:51,040
♪My greenness is not an excuse to be bullied♪

6
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:54,200
♪Spreading the wings and soaring, inviting recklessness at any moment♪

7
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:57,200
♪I do not fear the life of hardship♪

8
00:00:57,280 --> 00:01:00,040
♪For I shall solve all riddles destined for me♪

9
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:03,400
♪Great difficulties can summon the sea of courage♪

10
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:06,640
♪It's worth defending heroic spirits in the martial arts world♪

11
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:12,000
♪One smile is all it takes, I travel faraway with my spirited ballads♪

12
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:15,820
♪Chasing after the hot-blooded dreams♪

13
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,880
♪Growing old with a heart of gold♪

14
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,000
♪The journey ahead will leave scars♪

15
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:25,000
♪A life is only worth living with adventures♪

16
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:28,320
♪Conflicts are witnessed by the clashing of youths♪

17
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:31,080
♪Brushing against the blade of time♪

18
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:38,040
♪At the end of the universe, we embark on another journey yet again♪

19
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,760
♪Chasing after the hot-blooded dreams♪

20
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:43,760
♪Growing old with a heart of gold♪

21
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:46,680
♪The journey ahead will leave scars♪

22
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:50,400
♪A life is only worth living with adventures♪

23
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:53,120
♪Conflicts are witnessed by the clashing of youths♪

24
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:56,000
♪Brushing against the blade of time♪

25
00:01:56,400 --> 00:02:03,480
♪At the end of the universe, we embark on another journey yet again♪

26
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:15,940
[The Blood of Youth: Quest of Heroic Hearts]

27
00:02:15,980 --> 00:02:18,980
[Episode 10]

28
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:21,400
Greetings, Sect Leader.

29
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,520
The side effects

30
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:27,470
of your demonic arts are getting worse lately.

31
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,470
We must find the Skysplitter

32
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,470
to treat you quickly.

33
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,080
But

34
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:34,000
why must we use them

35
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,030
to find the Skysplitter?

36
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:37,520
They will be a nuisance.

37
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:39,840
Why don't I

38
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:41,560
just kill them?

39
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,400
They must not be killed.

40
00:02:44,710 --> 00:02:45,910
That's my bottom line.

41
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,030
I told you

42
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,800
that Weigui and the Skysplitter were related.

43
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,190
Giving them the fragments

44
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:56,030
is to help Weigui recall his memory.

45
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:57,520
Only he

46
00:02:57,870 --> 00:03:00,120
can lead us to the real Skysplitter.

47
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:05,800
Also,

48
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:07,680
you're not to act

49
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,470
without my permission.

50
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,240
But...

51
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:15,710
Yes.

52
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,900
Due to the side effects of the demonic arts,

53
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,710
my gender changes irregularly,

54
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:27,080
and it's happening more frequently lately.

55
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,560
It seems like

56
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:31,150
my time is running out.

57
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:52,000
Where is Ye Zhixin?

58
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,150
He went to the toilet, I suppose.

59
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:07,220
[I have left. I will wait for you in the corridor. Ye Zhixin]

60
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,280
Why did he go to the corridor alone?

61
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:15,310
I guess

62
00:04:15,590 --> 00:04:17,040
he wants to get the Skysplitter fragment

63
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,720
before the break of dawn.

64
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:21,560
Perhaps

65
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,120
he wants to be the strongest swordsman too?

66
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:23,800
Weigui,

67
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:25,270
do you know where the corridor is?

68
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,680
I remember roughly what it looks like.

69
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,240
I already told you everything yesterday.

70
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:35,000
The corridor is a place.

71
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,750
Its location is written in this book.

72
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:38,120
Let's go then.

73
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,430
Let's go.

74
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,420
Let's go.

75
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,270
We've been walking for several hours.

76
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:54,750
How come we are not there yet?

77
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,750
Miss Xiaohua,

78
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,600
are we heading in the right direction?

79
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,270
The book says it's just right in front.

80
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:04,240
[The Corridor]

81
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:04,870
See?

82
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,190
This is the corridor.

83
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:14,750
The door is ajar.

84
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,120
Someone must have been here.

85
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:17,600
Ye Zhixin?

86
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,270
Not necessarily.

87
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,950
It could be other people from the martial arts world.

88
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:25,750
It could also be people from Tianwaitian.

89
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,430
What are we waiting for?

90
00:05:27,630 --> 00:05:28,430
We should go inside.

91
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,120
I think this is the corridor.

92
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,720
After being tormented many times by the ox-head butcher

93
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,600
in the dream we had at Liuli Manor,

94
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:49,270
I feel unnerved

95
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:50,950
when I see the mist.

96
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,310
We are not familiar with the place.

97
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:56,920
Please

98
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:57,950
exercise caution.

99
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,750
Miss I-know-everything,

100
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:03,040
is there a creepy legend about this place?

101
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,430
Just speak frankly.

102
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,800
We can take it.

103
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:09,190
Legend has it

104
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:12,390
that this is a dangerous place.

105
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:14,000
They say

106
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,160
whoever enters the corridor

107
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,510
and comes out alive will have an unsound mind.

108
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,630
When we enter,

109
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:27,870
we must look after each other.

110
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,720
Don't get separated.

111
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,750
What are you writing?

112
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,870
What you owe me.

113
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,310
I don't have time to count everything now.

114
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:45,560
But in the future, I'll itemize everything clearly.

115
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:48,430
You'll have to pay for each of my services.

116
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,160
You!

117
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:55,160
A merchant only cares about their money.

118
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:56,480
Merchant?

119
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,510
Services ought to be compensated.

120
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:11,270
Why does it turn dark suddenly?

121
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,950
This is eerie.

122
00:07:20,430 --> 00:07:21,040
This place

123
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:23,390
is just as creepy as the dream in Liuli Manor.

124
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:24,680
What do you think?

125
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:29,600
Hua Xiaohua?

126
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:31,750
Weigui?

127
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:35,870
I can hear you.

128
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,720
Where are you?

129
00:07:38,310 --> 00:07:39,720
I can't see you at all.

130
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:41,830
I'm at the center of the corridor.

131
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,870
Me too.

132
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,190
Me too.

133
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,120
Don't worry.

134
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,630
There is only one path.

135
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,270
Just walk straight

136
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,430
and we will group up.

137
00:07:58,510 --> 00:07:59,430
Be careful.

138
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:00,240
- Okay. - Okay.

139
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,870
Why is the mist getting thicker?

140
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,830
Lei Lingze. Xiaohua.

141
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:57,510
Who are you?

142
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:01,320
You don't remember me.

143
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,240
I don't.

144
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,030
Who's there?

145
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:42,790
[One can be smart or ignorant, one article can be profound or shallow]

146
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:44,960
[An ignorant person can become smart with enough practice]

147
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:45,790
Isn't this

148
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:48,870
the information I recorded?

149
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:51,390
You're just a writer of tabloid press.

150
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,630
What makes you think you can be part

151
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:57,080
of the martial arts world or the Baixiao Hall?

152
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:00,150
You overestimated yourself.

153
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:02,510
Go back to where you come from.

154
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:07,270
No one will ever read the gibberish you wrote.

155
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:09,320
You shouldn't even live in this world.

156
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,270
Shut up.

157
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,630
This is not true.

158
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,120
This is not true!

159
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:36,840
Who are you?

160
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:38,440
I can ask you the same question.

161
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,150
Who are you?

162
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,390
I am Lei Lingze.

163
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:56,910
No,

164
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,550
you're not.

165
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:00,790
I am Lei Lingze.

166
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,550
Impossible.

167
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,200
It's futile.

168
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:12,960
You can't unsheathe it.

169
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,000
Curse it!

170
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:19,030
Don't you want to be the strongest swordsman?

171
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:22,150
Come.

172
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,670
Let me show you how to unsheathe a sword.

173
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:26,120
I want to be the strongest swordsman.

174
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:28,360
Come here.

175
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,200
Useless.

176
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,670
You can't even unsheathe your sword.

177
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:44,840
How can you kill?

178
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:46,390
How can you be the strongest swordsman?

179
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:56,270
It seems like you're dying to know who I am.

180
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:57,320
Is that so?

181
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:58,240
Although

182
00:11:58,910 --> 00:12:00,030
I don't know who you are,

183
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:02,670
I know

184
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:05,600
that I must kill you.

185
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:10,750
Perhaps you shouldn't have known about it.

186
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:15,790
Curse it.

187
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,390
Why can't I move?

188
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:31,720
What do you think?

189
00:12:32,150 --> 00:12:33,840
I prepared this for you.

190
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,960
Do you like it?

191
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:39,670
If you can't overcome your past fear,

192
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:41,000
you will not be able to move.

193
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:30,880
♪How can I make peace when time♪

194
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:34,000
♪Only leaves me with my shadow?♪

195
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:38,960
♪Yet the intertwining bonds in my life♪

196
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:42,240
♪Render me blind♪

197
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:47,160
♪I was once naive and innocent♪

198
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:50,440
♪Seeking a soul with whom to dance♪

199
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:55,400
♪Yet my life is like a wisp of smoke♪

200
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:58,560
♪Scattered by a gust of wind♪

201
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:01,560
♪In this life, I am not destined to be understood♪

202
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,840
♪But misunderstood♪

203
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:06,920
♪I do not know sincerity♪

204
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:11,680
♪If the river of time could flow back to its starting point♪

205
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:15,000
♪Let's not meet again♪

206
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:17,960
♪No one will be able to understand me♪

207
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,040
♪None will go as I wish♪

208
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:23,280
♪How I long for that one moment to last forever♪

209
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:28,000
♪All mortal obsessions turn into dusts of nothingness♪

210
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:31,200
♪Let's not meet in another life♪

211
